RC low-pass filter

ground 0

load "resistor.osdi"
load "capacitor.osdi"

model resistor resistor
model capacitor capacitor
model vsrc vsource

V1 (in 0) vsrc dc=0 type="pulse" val0=0 val1=1 delay=0 rise=1n fall=1n width=5u period=10u
R1 (in out) resistor r=1k
C1 (out 0) capacitor c=1n

control
  options rawfile="binary"
  analysis tran1 tran stop=20u step=10n
endc
